By

Updated Nov 21, 2023
Summary
Aasha and Brandon, the confirmed Perfect Match from season 8 of Are You The One?, split after the show ended. Aasha now has a podcast, while Brandon's current whereabouts are unknown. Amber and Remy, who were declared a Perfect Match despite never sitting together, have found success after the show. Amber participated in The Challenge and now co-hosts a reaction show, while Remy is focused on being a dad and building his social media following. Basit and Jonathan were a hidden Perfect Match and have gone on to pursue different paths. Basit advocates for the LGBTQ+ community, while Jonathan has become a professional hair stylist and makeup artist. Jonathan's relationship status is currently unknown.
